{"id":1097,"date":"2019-05-16T07:28:03","date_gmt":"2019-05-16T07:28:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/?p=1097"},"modified":"2019-05-16T07:30:42","modified_gmt":"2019-05-16T07:30:42","slug":"holographicdisplays","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/plugins-used\/holographicdisplays\/","title":{"rendered":"Holographic Displays"},"content":{"rendered":"<div>\n<p>Source: <a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\">https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/tutorial\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/543\/_0002_Tutorial.png\" alt=\"Tutorial\" width=\"57\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/commands-and-permissions\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/538\/_0004_Commands.png\" alt=\"Commands\" width=\"71\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/commands-and-permissions\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/539\/_0004_Permissions.png\" alt=\"Permissions\" width=\"77\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/symbols\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/550\/_0002_Symbols.png\" alt=\"Symbols\" width=\"57\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/variables\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/551\/_0001_Variables.png\" alt=\"Variables\" width=\"63\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/animations\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/549\/_0002_Animations.png\" alt=\"Animations\" width=\"73\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/filoghost\/HolographicDisplays\/wiki\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/540\/_0003_API.png\" alt=\"API\" width=\"31\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/filoghost\/HolographicDisplays\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/541\/_0002_Source.png\" alt=\"Source\" width=\"53\" height=\"28\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/571\/iconset_bug.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/issues\" rel=\"nofollow\">Report a bug<\/a>\u00a0|\u00a0<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/575\/iconset_help.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" \/>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/faq\" rel=\"nofollow\">Help &amp; FAQ<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h2 id=\"title-1\"><strong>Features<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Create floating text lines!<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/commands-and-permissions\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Floating icons<\/strong><\/a>!<\/li>\n<li>Fast and easy to use.<\/li>\n<li>Simple API for developers.<\/li>\n<li>Transform images into holograms with a single command.<\/li>\n<li>You can create your own\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/animations\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>animations<\/strong><\/a>!<\/li>\n<li>Includes the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fi.imgur.com%252fbBy4xYC.gif\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>animated rainbow color<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0&amp;u!<\/li>\n<li>Supports any\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/symbols\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>UTF-8 symbol<\/strong><\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>Can displays the amount of\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays\/pages\/variables\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>players online<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0in a BungeeCord server (supports RedisBungee)<\/li>\n<li>Supports Spigot 1.8 to 1.13.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"title-2\"><strong>Preview<\/strong><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/media-elerium.cursecdn.com\/attachments\/124\/570\/hd_cover.png\" alt=\"Preview\" width=\"605\" height=\"283\" \/><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title-3\"><strong>Plugins using Holographic Displays\u00a0(API)<\/strong><\/h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/bukkit-plugins\/touchscreen-holograms\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Touchscreen Holograms<\/strong><\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fdonations-holograms.1956%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Donations Holograms<\/strong><\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fcombatindicator.5834%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">CombatIndicator<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fholoshop.3522%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">HoloShop<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fholographic-scoreboard.2700%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Holographic-Scoreboard<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fholoplots.4880%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">HoloPlots<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fplaceholderhook-beta.3878%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">PlaceholderHook<\/a>\u00a0(more placeholders!)<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fperplayerholograms-great-donator-perk.6527%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">PerPlayerHolograms<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252frankupholograms.3216%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">RankupHolograms<\/a>\u00a0(for EZRanksLite)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/bukkit-plugins\/speechbubbles-reloaded\/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SpeechBubbles Reloaded<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fsurvivalgames.1351%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">SurvivalGames<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252finventoryfull-display-holograms-titles-actionbar-chat-messages-when-your-inventory-is-full.1059%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">InventoryFull<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252ffarming-utilities-farm-with-helpful-holograms-and-gui-75-off.6684%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Farming Utilities<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fcraft-bench-block.636%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Craft Bench Block<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"http:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/bukkit-plugins\/special-die-message\/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Special Die Message<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252ffireworksplus.2612%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">FireworksPlus<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"http:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/bukkit-plugins\/holographic-graves\/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Holographic Graves<\/a><\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fholographic-powerup-support_1-8-3.6079%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Holographic PowerUp<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title-4\"><strong>Servers using this plugin<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Trusted by\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fbstats.org%252fplugin%252fbukkit%252fHolographicDisplays\" rel=\"nofollow\">over 10.000\u00a0servers<\/a>, including some famous networks:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fminecade.com%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Minecade<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fmccentral.org%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Minecraft Central<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.uberminecraft.com%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Uberminecraft<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title-5\"><strong>Video<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/MCiNHy8jZas?wmode=transparent\" width=\"638\" height=\"358\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title-6\"><strong>Minecraft limitations<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Holograms will always rotate to follow the player&#8217;s view.<\/li>\n<li>You cannot change the text size. You can make it bold and uppercase to make it look bigger.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"title-7\"><strong>Credits<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Asdjke<\/strong>\u00a0for the awesome idea in vanilla (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=q1B19JvX5TE\" rel=\"nofollow\">video<\/a>).<\/li>\n<li><strong>bobacadodl<\/strong>\u00a0for making image support easier with\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/forums.bukkit.org\/threads\/lib-imagemessage-v2-1-send-images-to-players-via-the-chat.204902\/\" rel=\"nofollow\">this library<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li><strong>samczsun<\/strong>\u00a0for the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=http%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fserverpinger.2184\" rel=\"nofollow\">Server Pinger lib<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fwww.paypal.com%252fcgi-bin%252fwebscr%253freturn%253dhttp%253a%252f%252fdev.bukkit.org%252fbukkit-plugins%252fholographic-displays%252f%2526cn%253dAdd%2bspecial%2binstructions%2bto%2bthe%2baddon%2bauthor(s)%2526business%253dfiloghost%2540gmail.com%2526bn%253dPP-DonationsBF%253abtn_donateCC_LG.gif%253aNonHosted%2526cancel_return%253dhttp%253a%252f%252fdev.bukkit.org%252fbukkit-plugins%252fholographic-displays%252f%2526lc%253dUS%2526item_name%253dHolographic%2bDisplays%2b(from%2bBukkit.org)%2526cmd%253d_donations%2526rm%253d1%2526no_shipping%253d1%2526currency_code%253dEUR\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http:\/\/filoghost.me\/data\/donate-button.png\" alt=\"Donate\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Converting from other plugins<\/strong><br \/>\n<em>If you&#8217;re using the plugin\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fholograms.4924%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Holograms<\/a>\u00a0you can use\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fwww.spigotmc.org%252fresources%252fholograms-to-holographicdisplays-converter.27821%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">this converter<\/a>\u00a0to import the database (credits to saxon12).<\/em><\/p>\n<p><strong>Metrics<\/strong><br \/>\n<em>This plugin uses bStats, to track anonymous data about servers using this plugin. It will help the future developement, and has no impact on your server&#8217;s performance. If you really want to disable it, go to the folder \/plugins\/bStats\/config yml and set &#8220;enabled: false&#8221;.<\/em><\/p>\n<p><strong>Updater<\/strong><br \/>\n<em>By default, you will see update notifications when loading the server and when you join it, if you have the permission &#8220;holograms.admin&#8221;. You can disable the update checking at startup by setting update-notification: false in config yml.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Source: https:\/\/dev.bukkit.org\/projects\/holographic-displays \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0Report a bug\u00a0|\u00a0\u00a0Help &amp; FAQ Features Create floating text lines! Floating icons! Fast and easy to use. Simple API for developers. Transform images into holograms with a single command. You can create your own\u00a0animations! Includes the\u00a0animated rainbow color\u00a0&amp;u! Supports any\u00a0UTF-8 symbol. Can displays the amount of\u00a0players online\u00a0in a BungeeCord server (supports RedisBungee)&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1103,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[24],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1097"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1097"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1097\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1102,"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1097\/revisions\/1102"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/cdn.floydcraft.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1103"}],"wp:attachme